Name: MopGarden's Veggie Cart
About the game: MopGardenâ€™s Veggie Cart is a fast-paced, simulation game where you feed hungry bunnies lots of healthy vegetables! Can you feed them all in time? MopGarden, a variety Twitch streamer, has decided to feed all the local bunnies in her town. As business begins to boom, she moves her veggie cart to other surrounding areas, where the vegetable orders get faster, and faster , and FASTER . Features Play through 4+ different worlds, each with varying difficulties. Bunnies are hungrier and more demanding at different times of day! Test your visual skills and reaction time. As you progress through the game, it gets harder and harder to determine what the bunnies are ordering Look out for other pesky animals! Other animals will drop in to throw a wrench into the vegetable orders. No bad stuff! This game is completely free to play. No advertisements, in-app purchases, or anything of the sort. No animals were harmed in the making of this game!
